                    },
                    "text": "CVE-2022-22965 is fixed in 2.6.6; see the Spring blog for details.",
                    "html": "<p>CVE-2022-22965 is fixed in 2.6.6; see <a href=\"https://spring.io/blog/2022/03/31/spring-boot-2-6-6-available-now\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">the Spring blog for details</a>. </p>"
